com.clarkparsia.common.iterations.Iteration

Packages that use Iteration
com.clarkparsia.common.iterations Contains classes for defining and using Iterations. 
 

Uses of Iteration in com.clarkparsia.common.iterations
 

Subinterfaces of Iteration in com.clarkparsia.common.iterations
 interface PeekingIteration<T,E extends Exception>
          An iteration which exposes the next element it will return.
 

Classes in com.clarkparsia.common.iterations that implement Iteration
 class AbstractIteration<T,E extends Throwable>
          Abstract implementation of the Iteration interface providing an implementation for all the basic methods of the interface.
 class ArrayIteration<T,E extends Exception>
          Implementation of an Iteration backed by an array.
 class DelegatingIteration<T,E extends Exception>
          Implementation of an Iteration which delegates its methods to a child Iteration.
 class MultiIteration<T,E extends Throwable>
          An adapter to provide a single iteration over a list of iterations.
 class TransformException<T,IE extends Throwable,OE extends Throwable>
          Implementation of an Iteration which will apply a function to transform the exceptions of an inner iteration to a different exception type.
 class TransformIteration<I,O,E extends Throwable>
          Implementation of an Iteration which will apply a function to transform the results of an inner iterator to a different type.
